WEBVTT

00:07:29.723 --> 00:07:32.660
and kaleidoscopic diversity.

00:07:34.928 --> 00:07:38.836
Once change became my totalizing faith,

00:07:40.415 --> 00:07:41.817
I could be blind.

00:07:43.143 --> 00:07:46.677
I could fail to see change's consequences.

00:07:47.866 --> 00:07:49.803
I could overlook the importance

00:07:49.827 --> 00:07:52.929
of roots, traditions,
rituals, stability --

00:07:52.953 --> 00:07:54.296
and belonging.

00:07:55.501 --> 00:07:58.816
And the more fundamentalist I became

00:07:58.840 --> 00:08:02.582
in my worship of change and openness,